Websearcher — interactive browser-driven web research (PI mode).

This tab is a login shell. Type `claude` to start the websearcher session.

The session drives a headless Playwright browser (image-baked) for live web
research. Role + tools are auto-discovered when claude starts:

  /workspace/CLAUDE.md            the websearcher role prompt (symlink to role.md)
  /workspace/.tools-inventory.md  the live tool set (incl. the Playwright extras)

`browser_evaluate` is denied at the client layer (managed-settings) as a
prompt-injection guard; role.md names the denied tools.

Publish finished artifacts to /workspace/published/ via `manifest describe`.
